\n      return self.cli.send_cli(self.command, *args, **kwargs)\n             ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n    File \"./test/functional/test_framework/test_node.py\", line 1043, in send_cli\n      raise subprocess.CalledProcessError(returncode, p_args, output=cli_stderr)\n",
